      "content": "\"manage it\" doesnt mean anything when the pain is this bad. i've tried everything. i've done the meds, the physical therapy, the specialists... nothing works. it feels like i'm just being forced to endure this agony for no reason. sometimes i look at the silence of sleep and just wish it didn't have to end. like, wouldn't it be a relief to just... not be here? to finally have some peace?",
